@startuml

actor Client
participant "Client Portal" as ClientPortal
participant "Backend API" as Backend
participant "Notification Service" as NotificationService

Client -> ClientPortal: Login to Account
ClientPortal -> Backend: Authenticate Client
Backend -> ClientPortal: 200 Authenticated

Client -> ClientPortal: Browse Services & Availability
ClientPortal -> Backend: Get Available Time Slots
Backend -> ClientPortal: Return Available Services & Times
ClientPortal -> Client: Show Calendar & Service List

Client -> ClientPortal: Select Service & Time
ClientPortal -> Backend: Book Appointment Request
Backend -> Backend: Validate Slot Availability
Backend -> Backend: Create Appointment Record
Backend -> ClientPortal: 201 Appointment Booked
note right of Backend
  Appointment confirmed
  Sending notifications
end note
Backend -> NotificationService: Send Booking Confirmation
NotificationService -> Client: Email/SMS Confirmation
ClientPortal -> Client: Appointment Confirmed

@enduml
